com.kuka.roboticsAPI.params

Interface IParameterSetBuilder<T extends IParameterSetBuilder<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the parameter set builder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractParameterSetBuilder, ParameterSetBuilder, RobotParameterSetBuilder

    public interface IParameterSetBuilder<T extends IParameterSetBuilder<?>>
    Represents a parameter set builder (builder pattern). A parameter set is generated by build().
    This element is not in its final state and might change in future versions.
